values:
i havent written in while...man. im gettin as bad as josh...lol

anyways. we have a 3 day weekend. :)
i had a game last night, and tonight. 
the guys lost to dutchtown.
DUTCHTOWN.
ugh. sucks.

i have cheerleading all the time...another person quit during the game tuesday night.
we had 9 girls cheering tonight.  and. come to find out..we are having a stupid pep rally at the end of the month...so we have to do a routine or something. its gonna suck. and we are going to get booed.
i have a scheduled headache for that day.
i will not be at school.

my six month rule is over tomorrow. but guess who broke it? oh yes. i drove kara and sarah to the game tonight..haha what a rebel. one day before. we went to marble slab..haha sarah and kara..those girls had their mom...lol. lamos.

i went shopping at stonecrest today..got some new stuff from ae and bath and body works. i got some coco cabana shower gel...smells like suntan lotion..mmmm.

i wish cheerleading would end..i have like 8 more games. ugh.
ive been in a depressed mood lately. im not sure why. everything just gets me down, or hurts my feelings. or something. idk. it's weird.
oooo well.

ive skipped the last two nights of exercising. i need to force myself to start doing that again.

we rented the move 'bourne supremacy' the other day..ive been meaning to watch that..but ive had like no time. i need to do that tomorrow or monday.......
american idol starts tuesday...who's excited???

well..i gotta get up for church tomorrow.
night fellas.

well. i had to update this thing cause josh did.

i havent written in awhile. ive been pretty busy..cheerleading all the time, school, church.  and for the next month and a half im gonna have games on tuesday, friday and saturdays. practice on thursdays, and church on wednesday and sunday. so. basically i have mondays free...isnt that grand.

aaron let me borrow anchorman and dodgeball wednesday..i have yet to watch them cause ive had no time. so..i plan to watch them tomorrow after church. or. i might just take a nap.

i had a game tonight...we lost against stockbridge. again. i mean..i dont really care if we win, i just hate being behind 30 points and like having no chance at winning. the team just gives up and i feel bad for them. i mean..i know they are still trying. but.  idk. 
anyways..so me, aaron and kara went to eat at china king...then me and aaron stayed and talked for awhile. it was good..until he threw chinese food everywhere...lol. nah. it was fun.

well..josh had refuge tonight. :( i saw him earlier today at davids party. which was fun. but i could only stay for like 2 hours. he came to my game tuesday...:D..he's great.

kara got a car. its so cute...but she doesnt get her license for another two weeks...which sucks. BUT..next sunday i will be able to have people in my car...finally. the stupid 6 month thing is over! heck yes.

i signed up to take the ACT feb. 12.
im gonna have to register for my senior classes this month...crazy.

cheerleading...ugh. we've had 5 girls quit so far...maybe 6. one out with a bad knee...one in hollywood? idk. we had 10 girls tonight cheering. i dont even know whats going on? whatever. im tired of it...only 10 more games left. 20 if u count girls and boys....great. :/

well..im tired.
xoxo
<3


OJ. :D

well the past few days have been pretty busy...

monday i had to go up to the church around 10 and work..then we went to shanes for lunch, and afterwards me and sarah went to karas and watched 'blue collared comedy tour 2'. 
then i went by the nextel store to see if they could change the housing of my phone...they wouldnt do it.
 so. me, sarah and mrs. jana went to southlake mall to spend our giftcards, and get our phones changed. the met the guy who changed our phones Reza..or razzle dazzle. that was interesting meeting that guy...
afterwards we went to steak and shake..and then drove around a place...it was really sad...we remembered good times..and bad.  depressing..but ya know.

yesterday i went to Moe's and the movies with josh, jacob, kara and sarah. we saw Spanglish...it was alright...it was fun to hang out with everyone.

today..my dad called me at 11..and i had drop marisa off at my aunts house..then go to a neighborhood not to far away where my dad was working..and then go to the bank...papa johns...and back to my dads job..then i went to the tanning bed. home by 2:00.
now...i have nothing to do...and im bored.
friday night we are having our 'annual' new years eve party....
not looking forward to school...but we still have like 4 1/2 days left....lol. trying not to think about it...:\

well..i dont have anything interesting to talk about....
see ya.

Well..Christmas has come and gone for yet another year.

i got a digital camera. yay.
i also got a clear pink cell phone cover/housing. whatever.
gift cards...clothes..all good stuff. i got a tan membership from aaron. thank goodness. i needed that.

We've been out of school for a whole week...and we still have another week to go. :)
we went to the Varsity friday night...woke up christmas morning..santa was good to us. my family came over and we ate breakfast, and opened presents.
aaron came over and woke me up. i was happily sleeping on the couch lol. we hung out for awhile..played super mario on my super nintendo...lol. watched christmas vacation. i hadnt seen that before..it was funny. had some bad parts...my mom would be like "aaron!" and he would just laugh. it was funny...

today i went to church...then afterwards i went with josh to Bistro 41. it was pretty good. i finally met his friend craig. and we opened presents..:) he gave me the dvd Cold Mountain...a cute throw blanket..and a sweater from AE.:D i couldnt believe my mom let me go...that was a shocker.

oh! and i mentioned before i was gonna watch napoleon dynamite.  yeah.
me and kara saw it.
i laughed twice.
talk about disappointment.

im being forced to help tomorrow at the church at 10, cleaning out the new teen room.
good thing sarah is too. haha.

im going by the nextel place tomorrow to get my case put on hopefully...then the tanning place.
well..i have to finish doing the dishes...:/

.Hannah.

Take the quiz: "Which Laguna Beach Character are You?"

Christina
You have strong morals and respect your friends. Singing and Acting are a passion... You are very smart though also. hm. im no actress....

im not sure why im feelin down. but oh well i guess...

kara and sarah should be here in a few minutes. we are going to exchange christmas presents...we all know what we are getting each other...sorta weird. but it works for us. :)

then we are going to watch napoleon dynamite. ive heard so much about this movie. how funny it is...so..i hope im not disappointed.

ive been drinking water for the last three days. and i havent been hungry...so i havent been eating as much, and ive been exercising.  im gonna keep this up for the next 2 weeks. and we'll see how it goes....

no more school for 2 weeks :D
exams went alright...
algebra-88...u.s. history-79 :\..anatomy-89..spanish-94..and i think i did alright on my english essay.
but..its all over...:)
my dads family is coming over tomorrow for christmas. we usually have theirs the sunday before christmas. but im still going to church of course....;)
ive had to wrap presents tonight....ive done nothing all day. talked on the phone for awhile with josh. i wish i couldve gone to refuge tonight...but ill see him tomorrow so..its okay. hehe.

im watching 'a white christmas'..its an old movie...i was telling josh about it today, and it just came on. its good...

my sister shannon is coming tomorrow..i havent seen her since the summer. im excited i get to see my big sis. :)

well..im gonna go find a blanket, lay on the couch and watch the movie...
<3
hannah

yep. ive done nothing all weekend.  ive been quarantined at home with pink eye for basically 3 days. if i dont get some human contact other than my family soon..i might go crazy.
i dunno how i got it...but i woke up friday and my eye was all red..but i still went to school, and in 2nd period i went up to the office cause it was bothering me. they sent me home cuz its contagious or whatever. so. i went to my moms work, then went to zaxbys. lol. i couldnt go to my game cuz i hadnt been at school for at least half the day....so that night me and mom went to kroger, then rented 'the terminal' 
saturday...went to kroger again..i had to make my trifle thing that i always make...then i layed on the couch all day and watched the entire season of 'americas next top model' on VH1..from 1-9. lol... the finale comes on wednesday night..i gotta tape it cuz im all caught up and i wanna see who wins.
today..i was gonna go to church..but i woke up late...then decided there wasnt really a reason to go for just the big service. so i didnt. we ordered dominos..and watched like 3 shows of 'date my mom' or something on mtv.
then..i talked to josh for awhile...and studied for spanish. our exam is basically broken up into three days...and 20% is tomorrow, i have to say my story..then stay after school and take the other 20% i missed friday. fun.

im really not looking foward to exams....gah they suck.

ive layed around this entire weekend. and i realized im getting quite large. i need to cut back on the calories. haha. oh well.

well...i gotta go get ready for church..they are having some christmas program tonight. josh cant go...:(  sad.
but as he says..itll be ok. :) oj.

<3

seven more days. yes.

well. ive been sorta busy the past few days. monday...school..my sisters chorus concert...

tuesday...cheerleading at 6:45am. of course..i set my alarm clock wrong. i hear my phone ringing..didnt want to pick it up cuz im like asleep..then im thinking...why is my phone ringing so early? looked at the clock. 6:45.  went to look at who called...of course it was the greatest guy ever, josh.  i called him back. he helped me thru my mild panic attack cuz i was like half asleep still and practice had already started.. so i just went and took a shower, and got to practice at like 7:30. school was alright...then we had a game against fayette county. girls won, boys lost. like always. the boys tried hard tho...just lost it in the end. :( 

today..school went by slowly as usual..i had a test in anatomy. i think i did pretty good. review game in U.S. 1st place. oh yes. those bonus points will help tomorrow. i went to kroger after school...then came home..had some homework. and went to the nail place. that took forever and i was late to church by about 20 min. but they had just started. so it was alright. church was good...then like everyone went to shanes. except for my my girls..kara and sarah. sad, too much homework. but anyways shanes was fun...lol. all the guys are so funny. and the food was really good tonight..i guess cuz i hadnt eatin since like 1. but it was still great as usual.
im really glad ive met all those guys and become good friends. :)
they all went to see blade 3 tonight after shanes..but of course. i couldnt go. but i think like 10 guys went...male bonding. thats always good.

aw i got a new purse tonight. jacob 'owed' me one from like 2 years ago. and he got me a reversable one from aeropostale. its so cute...the inside is green, and the outside is white. then u can flip it and i can have a green purse.

exams are coming up...:\.
i have 2 games this weekend...at lovejoy friday night, and newnan saturday night. -sigh-
i just remembered i have practice tomorrow....ugh..

well...im tired. so i guess i should get to bed.
goodnight.
<3

thinking of you...OJ. :)

the last few months have been flyin by...its already december and christmas is 3 weeks away...

i just got back from shopping..went to belks, payless, bath & body works, and famous footwear. i got some cute black shoes, and lipgloss. i suppose i should've waited till christmas...but oh well.

the past few months have been great...i guess thats why they've gone by so quickly. ive had the best time....:) olivejuice ;)
cheerleading has been keeping me pretty busy...so has school. newspaper..etc. 


ah..i love this season.

i love hearing him sing that...

well..i havent written in awhile. nothing major has happened...
im tired of cheerleading...well. actually its some of the people on the team. but whatever. 
we still have about 5 more days off school...yay. :)

my dad woke me up at 9:20 this morning? not sure why. he wanted to tell me what he had planned for the day. lol. we are going to eat with my mom somewhere around 12:30...then we are going to the movies to see 'christmas with the kranks' or something like that. my dad is the biggest tim allen fan ever. he always has been. hes been to the home improvement set and all that stuff...crazy.

well. i had a game last night at stockbridge. we lost. bad.  but it was fun...josh, jacob, kara, harrison and sarah came. then we all went to ihop, minus harrison. but it was still a good night...:D

tomorrows thanksgiving...family is coming over.

the weather right now is really bad...i had a tree limb fly past my window earlier. scared me to death. all this stuff was just bouncing off the house.  and we are about to drive in it.  buuut..my dad said it should stop soon. so who knows.
ive been watchin ER all morning...exciting.

well i guess i better get ready to leave.

<3

geez. i want to change my password for my journal but it says that the new password ive chosen is "a bad password and not a dictionary word" ? what is that about?  it's a bad password?  gahlee. lol

anyways.  well. its been a long week....tomorrow i have cheerleading at 6:45am again...at the beginning of practice it was canceled...but at the end..for some reason we have it again.
practice was crazy. oooh the drama. it's unbelievable. people getting kicked off....then coming back again. i dont know whats goin on. it wasnt like this last year...if it had been i probably wouldnt have cheered this year.
tomorrow night we have our first game at Luella. sorta nervous. but...at least we wont be doing halftime for another week. yes.
josh is coming to my game...:)  yay.
so far..i dont have practice saturday morning...but i still have to be up at the school by 11:00 for the whole Howard Bahr thing...i was really going to it so i could get out cheerleading for an hour...but now..i'm going just to go...plus..i think we get extra credit. so..it could be interesting.

the paper comes out tomorrow....
and we get a entire week off school. heck yeah.
one more day.

i was just thinking...i'm gonna have a really busy week...
its gonna be crazy.
but then we have a whole week off....so ya know.
oh well i guess, i hate having nothing to do...

i have cheerleading practice wednesday. and friday morning. 6:45am.
afternoon practice tues. and thurs.
a game friday and saturday night. and  practice saturday morning.
i have to stay after school monday and wednesday for newspaper...
it's insane.

i gotta see if i can go to refuge tonight....sorta scared to ask. but oh well i guess.
well..my mom is home...she brought home subway..im savin it for dinner tho...
ttyl
-hannah
whew.

well..things are going good... all the drama has died down for now....and thats always good. so ya know.

im ready for the weekend...oh and my dad informed me that on saturday im taking my sister to kroger sometime between noon and 5 because they are having this special thing there with free samples. i thought that was hilarious...my dad was depressed he has to work...my family is crazy.

uugh..im probably going to get in trouble when my mom gets home....we got this piece of paper talking about a booster club meeting last week..and the meeting was tonight. well of course i forgot to give it to my mother...and i called her after practice but she was on the home phone and her cell phone at the same time...not sure why. but i told my dad to tell her about the meeting tonight. and he didnt. she went out to eat with some friends for a birthday dinner...i guess it wouldnt be a big deal cuz its just a booster club meeting..but shes the treasurer this year. so idk if she was like really supposed to be there. ...:/. i always forget to give stuff to my mom..or tell her people called for her. yep...i feel the punishment coming.

well..today...school was boring...then i had cheerleading...layed in the tanning bed..and then i went to get some gas. over by kroger. i need to get my nails done really badly. they are like...ugh looking from the tanning bed. but i only have like 2 more visits...so i figure ill get them done around friday.

i have all this reading i need to do for school...im behind on last weeks reading for fletchers class...and i have 4 more chapters to read for this week...so..thats about 100+ pages. due friday. i guess i'll read thursday night. the book is so unbelievably boring..and i fall asleep everytime i try to read it.
i also have to read huckleberry finn for nettles class...that book isnt too bad tho...i have 4 chapters to read before friday. i'll read those either before or after church tomorrow. it shouldnt take long.
i also have to say my story for spanish thursday or friday...ugh. this whole year ive been really good about doing things early so im not procrastinating. yeah. all that went down the drain about 2 weeks ago. im getting lazy. :/
friday i have to wear my 'skeleton' shirt all day. its gonna suck...i have to get a paper signed every class period saying i wore it without wearing a jacket or sweatshirt over it....uuugh.
we got our progress reports today...3 a's and 3 b's. not too bad i guess.

well im goin over to sarahs real quick..she found some old choir tapes...lol im like in 1st grade...and josh is in it....i gotta see this....;)

-hannah

Today is Josh's Birthday! the big 2-2...lol  yup...i wish i could go eat with his family tonight. but ya know. it'll be alright. i guess ill give him his present sunday....:)

well school was pretty interesting today..a kid got beat up...blood everywhere..doors..floor...pretty gross. school went by pretty quickly...this whole week has gone by fast. 2 more weeks of school and thanksgiving break. an entire week off.

i had to watch my sister and her friend tonight...so sarah is probably coming over later..and we are gonna order pizza and rent a movie...

ugh. im so sick of these popup adds. for some reason the past few days they will not go away. i think my dad got rid of the popup blocker or we havent updated it or something.  geez.

tomorrow i have cheerleading....10-1..:( then im goin shoppin with my mom...it should be interesting. :/

Happy Birthday Josh!!!  :)

-poca...hehe

Well. its finally here. and all this election stuff will be over....thank goodness.

no school today...and i woke up around 9:30. what is up with that? i have nothing to do today but laundry...and i guess cleaning. boring. 

well..i had a good weekend...oh.i have an embarressing story from saturday....
ok. i wanted to go to payless to get some shoes...so i drive all the way to jonesboro road...go to get out of my car..and i had forgotten my shoes. its like the 4th time ive done that..but ive always been close enough to drive home and get some. i blame it all on josh. lol i was talkin to him as i went out the door...and i forgot to grab some. geez.
boys.
so anyways...i call sarah cuz im just dyin laughin and i had to tell someone...so. i just went inside without any shoes on...bought a pair of shoes..and walked out. i felt ridiculous..but oh well i guess.
sunday i woke up late and missed sunday school..so i went to to church...went to southlake mall...came home and went trick or treating in lakehaven. josh, jacob and ashley met me and kara and we all walked around. i was pocahontas...and kara was a cowgirl. ...afterwards we went to mcdonalds...and kara had to go..so me and josh watched full house...it was fun..:)
i got to hear josh play guitar and sing last night....yay. lol

well..im goin to meet jacob at eastlake diner...

*xoxo*

i just got home from seein the grudge with kristen,josh and katie.. gahlee. it was the scariest weirdest movie. it didnt really have a storyline...or at least i didnt understand it if there was one. lol. its ok though...i didnt really care about the movie anyways. :)  lol but anyways. i thought we were gonna die comin home....there was this whole line of cars and kristen gets near the front and like cuts in front of a guy...it was hilarious. lol he was like layin on his horn...she locked her doors in case he decided to jump out of his car...haha. what am i? an oven?? lol haha.

but anyways...the fall festival is tomorrow..me and sarah are workin either the cotton candy..or snow cones from 11-1. yawl should try to come...it starts at 11 and ends at 3. at glenhaven baptist.

well..i dont have much to right about...its just been a very good day...
hannah

well..ive haven't written in awhile...so i thought i would give an update....

i had a great weekend...
friday- i didnt go to school...i didnt feel too good cuz i was sick like all week. so i slept...and i couldnt go to the last football game cuz the air was all damp. and i had no voice as it is. soo..i went to applebees with my parents instead...
saturday- went to 6 flags...:) it was so fun. i loved hanging out with everyone...we only rode about 5 rides...lol but it didnt matter....we went in the haunted house...lol. i wouldve been so scared if sarah and kristen didnt look so funny...runnin around screaming their heads off. haha. i also had another reason i wasnt scared :)...lol. but anyways i had an awesome time at 6 flags...then we went to wendys and went thru the drive thru and sat outside cuz the inside was closed. the fast and the furious cars gathered beside us in the Kmart parking lot...lol. and a church van came and the girls were taken pics of josh...haha. oh well. i guess i can understand. lol.
sunday- church..frontera...church...phone till 3am. even tho. i was talking to myself for 5 min. before i realized.....lol. :)

monday...school was alright. afterwards i stayed after to take my spanish and U.S. history tests i missed friday. i know i failed fletchers test. ugh. i read thursday night...and i couldnt remember anything. i think i did alright on the spanish test.  we were supposed to go to Glenhaven..but it was canceled. :( i guess they are gonna re-schedule it.
so..i then went to the tanning bed and came home. dinner...tv...fell asleep around 10:30...woke up at about 12:30..checked my voicemail. and went back to bed.

today..school again. nothing special. sort of a long day...plus i had cheerleading. ugh. i dread it. but i dont have it thursday :) yay. afterwards...i went to the tanning bed and kroger. i bought marisa's potato chips...and a bag of parmesan goldfish and orange fanta for myself. yum.
sooo..im gonna watch all my shows tonight...lol. how sad.
im gonna go eat my goldfish.....:)

ttyl
x*o*x*o

yesterday was my birthday...it was good. i brought a cookie cake for journalism..then i got called up to the front office before lunch, and my mom had brought me shanes...i was so surprised..:) it was good. after school i had cheerleading till 5..then went home and my mom had made me my fav. dinner. mmm mmm. and she gave me some presents...i got some clothes and earrings..my aunt gave me a thing for tanning. 10 times in 2 months for the superbed. yay. now i wont glow when im at my basketball games cheerin...lol
then i went to church..and shanes afterwards. it was fun...everyone sang happy birthday to me..and it was quite embarressing. lol. well...aaron got me some earrings, a photo album thing, and a bear with a shirt on that says "do these  make my butt look big?" ugh. lol and josh got me the bethany dillon cd...:) ive been wantin it forever. thanks yawl..

well..im excited about this weekend....tomorrow night is the last football game. :( but it should be fun...then saturday is 6 flags! yay. everything worked out. im so happy. its gonna be alotta fun...:D

my voice is totally gone. i sound hilarious. today this guy stepped on my foot...i was like ow ow ow...and nothing came out but like a high squeak. i sounded like a seal. everyone laughed at me....lol it was funny...
after school i had to retake a math test...i think i did alot better than the first time..i'll know tomorrow what i got on it. so afterwards i went to cheerleadin for like 30 min..and for some reason practice ended at 5..so we picked up our cookie dough and i left. i went to my moms work to give my aunt's cookie dough to her...then to the burges house. i felt like a delivery person. lol.

but yeah...my mom wont be home till later tonight..and neither will my dad. my sister told me she was going somewhere..but i dont remember where. that could be bad....oh well.
im gonna be so bored tonight...i need to read my book for U.S...but i really dont want to.

well..i just talked to kristen and i think she might be spendin the night friday..aw fun.
im gonna go...ttyl

hannah

today started off good..then bad...then good again.
well..i got up around 8:20 this morning...i went to bed last night around 10:30. I think I o'd on some benedryl. i sorta guesstimated the amount i should take. ha. oh well. but..thankfully my dad was home this mornin and wrote me a note so i would be excused from first period. so...i got to talk to josh before school..which of course started the day off good. and i went to school before 2nd period. well. i get to school and it starts pourin down rain. i mean hard too. i sat in my car for a few min. hopin it would stop...but it didnt. it got a little lighter, so i finally walked inside. it took forever. and i was soakin wet by the time i got inside. and thankfully i had a sweatshirt in my car, so i just took that off when i went inside...so it wasnt as bad. but my pants were still soaked. soo..2nd and 3rd period are sorta a blur...and 4th..i got my story done, did some stuff on the computer for the newspaper and laid on the floor the rest of class. idk..i felt really weak. so..i tried to take a nap. didnt really work...i had to help fix problems on peoples computers and stuff...then..had lunch. then 5th and 6th.
after school i had to go to a math tutorial, cause i failed a test last week (67 :\)and we are getting to make it up thursday...so i went over my test with ms. cooper...and went to cheerleading practice for an hour.
finally came home...and ate dinner. my grandparents came over so they could give me my b'day present. which i got pearberry and sweet pea moisturizer, and spray. good stuff.

so..tomorrow im going to kroger before school so i can get some cupcakes or somethin for journalism. we find any excuse to bring food in that class..so i figure my birthday is a pretty good one? :D
yep. ill be 17 tomorrow...actually...in about 30 min. but whos counting? i was born at 4:10pm....but still. haha.

boston is winning ! 4-2 right now....i hope they win. yankees have gone to the world series like 8 times out of the past 9 years....hehe

well..im gonna head up to my room. i gotta leave about 7:55 tomorrow..and thats usually when i get up. :) lol
ttyl
love.

that song is in my head...we heard it at zaxbys..now i cant stop singing it.

i felt like updating this thing...so. i talk about my weekend.

Friday- school..blah. then i came home for awhile...went to blockbuster and rented the movie 'envy' this was horrible..i didnt watch half of it. after blockbuster i went over to ritz nails to talk to sarah..cuz she was getting her nails done. and i ran over a curb. i thought it was hilarious, it was over by mcdonalds and there were like 10 cars in the drive thru..and they all saw me. im a loser. lol ....anyways. then we went back to my house. we ordered pizza from papa johns at 6:30. it didnt get to my house till almost 10. the guy got lost or something..idk. but we didnt have to pay for it. so oh well.

Saturday- had cheerleadin camp from 9-3. i had to go to kroger before i went up to the school to get oranges. lol. we learned our dance...*shake it like a salt shaker* haha. how embarressing. not looking forward to doing that dance for halftime.......so..i went home..took a nap cuz i was tired. then got up, took a shower and went to Refuge. Josh did awesome of course...:) and it was a lot of fun. me, kara, jacob, and josh hung out till kara's dad came and got her..so i had to leave too. but still..it was alotta fun. and hopefully this saturday we are all going to six flags...

today..got up and went to church. it was freezing in the sanctuary or whatever. and i was hungry and tired. lol but oo well. i didnt think josh was comin to church. but he came before it started. yeah. he knew what was best for him. lol afterwards me, sarah and kara went to zaxbys...and we had quite a good conversation. too bad our parents wont let us go......ugh.

well...im gonna go take a nap before church tonight...
